data.description: This stunning 3-story townhouse is located in a gated community and offers over 3100 square feet of luxurious living space. With its double oven, marble countertops, and updated fixtures, the kitchen is a chef's delight. The open floor plan creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family. Freshly painted walls add to this charming space to call your own. Agents, please read private remarks.
